Package org.apache.nemo.runtime.executor.data.partitioner

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Partitioner<K extends Serializable>
    This interface represents the way of partitioning output data from a source task.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataSkewHashPartitioner
    An implementation of Partitioner which hashes output data from a source task appropriate to detect data skew.
    DedicatedKeyPerElementPartitioner
    An implementation of Partitioner which assigns a dedicated key per an output data from a task.
    HashPartitioner
    An implementation of Partitioner which hashes output data from a source task according to the key of elements.
    IntactPartitioner
    An implementation of Partitioner which makes an output data from a source task to a single Partition.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DedicatedKeyPerElement
    Declares that all of the designated keys for each element in a Partitioner is dedicated for the element.
